{"tid":1680303,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"1031 海洋公園萬聖節全員罷工","createTime":"2019-10-28T17:26:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-30T12:07:29.000Z","uid":66971,"like":65,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"d028d147c5a9a331dc5efd33bf3783e7a6b8d815","tid":1680303,"uid":66971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T17:26:10.000Z","msg":"事源 <a href=\"https://lih.kg/1679155\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1679155</a><br />\n同埋 <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/1729746950596616/posts/2471407496430554?sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F1729746950596616%2Fposts%2F2471407496430554%3Fsfns%3Dmo&d=SKXI%2FGePWbtdtN3kaacFPxURuvs7l%2FVEN9tydxl6KII%3D&h=81563456\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/1729746950596616/posts/2471407496430554?sfns=mo</a><br />\n罷工/ 罷演不罷工。<br />\nHalloween已經到嚟到最後階段，只淨四天的演出，其實已經没有商討的空間，大家發起呢個行動嘅目的喺咩呢？大家仲想爭取D咩？<br />\n提提大家，罷演不罷工對此立場&quot;中立&quot;的海洋公園並不是一個湊效的方法，反而奉上一個機會俾公園對大家作出罰懲。<br />\n<br />\n於正門靜坐亦對各位有危險及風險，介時人數眾多變成公眾活動，公園真係報警， 喺咪所有同事都可以應承擔呢個風險？<br />\n<br />\n罷工可以表達我哋對公園處理呢件事嘅手法不滿， 反對公園扼殺言論/創作自由及對表演者的不尊重！<br />\n我哋用行動証明我哋有足夠影響力影響哈囉喂嘅運作，<br />\n我哋喺哈囉喂嘅持份者，員工並唔係Condom! <br />\n而且確保大家嘅安全又可以顯現到我哋嘅影響力。<br />\n<br />\n31/10 海洋公園萬聖節全&quot;員&quot;罷工！<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/events/750926715319175/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fevents%2F750926715319175%2F&d=SKXI%2FGePWbtdtN3kaacFPxURuvs7l%2FVEN9tydxl6KII%3D&h=18a54690\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/events/750926715319175/</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/A8fgoBS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FA8fgoBS.jpg&h=61d35617&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dO723BS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdO723BS.jpg&h=e28c3bbd&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4656333806f7eebcd49009fe409219a19ba9993c","tid":1680303,"uid":66971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T17:28:08.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"8c8efbf49d353f00b62f7f88b31e18b5205de487","tid":1680303,"uid":66971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T17:28:21.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"bf335a0fa4a701f2b36206d3c034dfe901da5b48","tid":1680303,"uid":66971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T17:28:31.000Z","msg":"3"},{"pid":"f47e13378ed0f17c0b0af70f603531a2b4a45bdb","tid":1680303,"uid":66971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T17:28:41.000Z","msg":"4"},{"pid":"05e6ec7faf0ba2e3f78c9967ad5bc8622fee0a01","tid":1680303,"uid":66971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T17:28:51.000Z","msg":"5"},{"pid":"60a484cb1f5b2a3b8325a905302e1edcd0ea3ec7","tid":1680303,"uid":39911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T17:28:55.000Z","msg":"係先好"},{"pid":"964b3bb438b923c9dd7f3906589a1e4fa4b436ea","tid":1680303,"uid":66971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T17:29:01.000Z","msg":"6"},{"pid":"3e0b04f9e378e47ae8ad839fa2f9165d8f52c3cf","tid":1680303,"uid":66971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T17:29:15.000Z","msg":"7"},{"pid":"398db203ed9936a50522501d04166cac0b759cca","tid":1680303,"uid":29969,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T17:29:24.000Z","msg":"仲諗住31號去添"},{"pid":"1baf63e5a53122b17e580948d5e4951bcdffdd6a","tid":1680303,"uid":66971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T17:29:27.000Z","msg":"8"},{"pid":"020d1a0197cceeb249bfcc0e8f75a7aa6b1c16b8","tid":1680303,"uid":66971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T17:29:37.000Z","msg":"9"},{"pid":"6ec7a5c3e88aabfcff5b065421ed9aa7e693ac1c","tid":1680303,"uid":66971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T17:29:47.000Z","msg":"10"},{"pid":"96fc794